headline: GTA Online
subtitle: TALKING SHOP
content:
Dress up and deck out with an ever-changing range of designer clothes and urbane artwork for your Penthouse, all exclusive to the Diamond Casino store.

You are the one percent, so act like it: flaunt it, wear it, nail it to your walls. Don’t like art? Don’t own it. That’s minimalism, baby. So in right now. Because at the Diamond, you’re always in fashion.
